      %h1.scrollimation.scale-in My Works
      %p
        These are some of the projects I've worked on over the years.
    / ==== Portfolio Filters ====
    #filter-works
      %ul
        %li.active.scrollimation.fade-right.d1
          %a{"data-filter" => "*", :href => "#"} All
